    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reality is a matter of <strong>perspective</strong>; you can't trust both of your eyes! Look through your right eye to reveal hidden messages, demonic entities, and paths that don't exist in the &quot;real&quot; world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145790/extras/17f1446ec5dd545c3e47d66b49174262.poster.avif?t=1768931830\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145790/extras/17f1446ec5dd545c3e47d66b49174262.webm?t=1768931830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145790/extras/17f1446ec5dd545c3e47d66b49174262.mp4?t=1768931830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your left eye ONLY when necessary. Or else you will face your fate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145790/extras/6bae18d9417d56b41fef7be80be96b5c.poster.avif?t=1768931830\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145790/extras/6bae18d9417d56b41fef7be80be96b5c.webm?t=1768931830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145790/extras/6bae18d9417d56b41fef7be80be96b5c.mp4?t=1768931830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Staring too long with your left eye attracts things that live in the evil world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145790/extras/2ab98531ac803f6e2bbfb524856b001d.poster.avif?t=1768931830\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145790/extras/2ab98531ac803f6e2bbfb524856b001d.webm?t=1768931830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145790/extras/2ab98531ac803f6e2bbfb524856b001d.mp4?t=1768931830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Either Eye</i></strong><i> </i>is a puzzle psychological horror game. You are trapped in a world that appears peaceful, but a dark reality festers just beneath the surface. To survive, you must master the art of fractured vision.</p>",
